            <lg xml:id="TK1231">
<l>ciṟumai namakkoḻiyac cēṭceṉṟā ruḷḷi</l>
<l> naṟumalar nāṇiṉa kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While we endure the unbearable sorrow, your eyes weep for him who is gone afar, and shun (the sight of) fragrant flowers.</l>
